    "Overall, for any given turn, the LLM has to optimize one, and only one, of the following dialogue behavior objectives:",
    "• Plan Navigation.",
    "To guide the user through the plan, the LLM learns a training objective L N av to navigate the plan steps in either direction.",
    "The LLM always responds with an instruction that the user needs to follow.",
    "• Plan-grounded QA."
  ],
